                                        ],
                                        "body": "<div><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#solid_masonry_unit\">Solid</a> fuel-burning <span class=\"u-italic\">appliances</span> shall be provided with <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#combustion_air\">combustion air</a></span> in accordance with the <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#appliance_vented\">appliance</a></span> <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#manufacturer_s_installation_instructions\">manufacturer's installation instructions</a>. Oil-fired <span class=\"u-italic\">appliances</span> shall be provided with <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#combustion_air\">combustion air</a></span> in accordance with NFPA 31. The methods of providing <span class=\"u-italic\"><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#combustion_air\">combustion air</a></span> in this chapter do not apply to <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#fireplace\">fireplaces</a>, <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#fireplace_stove\">fireplace stoves</a> and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#direct-vent_appliance\">direct-vent <span class=\"u-italic\">appliances</span></a>. The requirements for <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#combustion\">combustion</a> and <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/2/definitions#dilution_air\">dilution air</a> for gas-fired <span class=\"u-italic\">appliances</span> shall be in accordance with <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/general-services-administration/irc-2024/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">Chapter 24</a>.</div>",
